## "Silence"

Peter says.

"Do you know what I have here?"

He waves your bill. You know it's over. Everything you worked for will be gone in a few moments.

"Don't lie to me. I can always add little lines next to your grades." He waves your transcript.

"It seems we couldn't afford to give everyone free laundry this year, and do you want to know why?"
